{"tid":1026176,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"北海道車禍下半身麻痺   港警高層李志恒康復良好已返港","createTime":"2019-02-18T02:15:31.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-18T07:17:20.000Z","uid":184679,"like":3,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"94fcaff50c07d409cb084212cfc19e71b9802a86","tid":1026176,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-18T02:15:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20190217/large/17la3p08.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20190217%2Flarge%2F17la3p08.jpg&h=a9f08883&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n去年聖誕節在日本北海道自駕遊期間遇車禍、頸椎受重傷的警務處高級助理處長、刑事及保安處處長李志恒（圖），在當地留醫逾個半月後，傷勢逐漸好轉，經醫生檢查評估狀況後，認為適合乘飛機，於上周三（13日）在妻子陪同下返港就醫，現時在麥理浩復康院接受復康治療。<br />\n<br />\n李志恒（54歲）返港後翌日，警隊「一哥」盧偉聰曾經到醫院探望。盧偉聰昨日早上透露，李志恒經瑪麗醫院初步檢查後，已於前日轉至麥理浩復康院進行一連串復康及物理治療。<br />\n<br />\n事發於去年12月25日聖誕節，當日下午，李志恒與親友一行7人到北海道旅遊，其所乘的車輛在小樽與余巿之間的赤井川村393號國道，與藝人曾志偉駕駛的車輛相撞。李受重傷由直升機送到醫院做手術，同車親友也受傷送院。<br />\n<br />\n意外中曾志偉兩條肋骨骨裂，他其後講述事發經過，聲稱李志恒所乘的車輛，意外發生時行駛在來回行車線的中間，當時雪地十分濕滑，路的兩旁更是懸崖。突然李志恒的車直衝過來，曾志偉的座駕無法避開而被撞。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20190217/20614415\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20190217%2F20614415&d=8lKb2kYWDOzPE5G8cc2TgA4SWcZegttS7JwdJctbizM%3D&h=812aff20\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20190217%2F20614415&h=4794b517\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20190217/20614415</a>"},{"pid":"8158c6aea9110d10cc79a5d63bc146ec3cc49c84","tid":1026176,"uid":28195,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-18T02:16:56.000Z","msg":"如果喺大陸車禍的話，一早返香港醫喇"},{"pid":"24b9618e3ffeccced5f8542800739c617fb06a16","tid":1026176,"uid":197563,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-18T02:21:20.000Z","msg":"長命百歲<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n百病纏身<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/censored.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1cca818c558e082125575c16c12f114e5430ab73","tid":1026176,"uid":93986,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-18T02:23:46.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">打和 ,Super!</span></span>"},{"pid":"c9a1e7d17700cc323b102bcfca33c563a6995f75","tid":1026176,"uid":53026,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-18T07:17:20.000Z","msg":"提早退休？"}]}